snippet.title: 125 MONKEY GAMES - MiniLD 50
snippet.description:
A demake of the monkey target mini-game from Super Monkey Ball.

Made in a weekend for the 50th MiniLD, the theme was "demakes".
(http://www.ludumdare.com/compo/minild-50/?action=preview&uid=13822)

Programming & Audio - Mark Wonnacott
Graphics - Claire Morley
